<br>
I said it before, let me point it out again:  paladin utility is nice, true.  But it's not really useful when you group with a shaman or druid.  They can do pretty much all the &quot;utility&quot; stuff that we can, and they can do it better than we can when we're all the same level.<br>
<br>
Haste - paladins can do it for themselves, shamans can do it for everyone in the group.<br>
healing - paladins can do it some, but all the priest classes can do more healing sooner.<br>
root - all the priest classes can root before paladins can.  Druids can snare, which is really handy.<br>
<br>
